This paper discusses neural network models and optimization techniques, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper's focus on backpropagation and loss functions further supports these sub-categories.
